    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to a world consumed by darkness. Take charge of the fight against the Lord of Darkness, whose army of skeletons spreads chaos and destruction. This is a turn-based strategy game with a deep storyline, where every decision you make impacts not only the outcome of battles but the fate of the entire world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to challenge the darkness?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302960/extras/a6952e45afe6f83b21206107341c3c48.avif?t=1745446066\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302960/extras_big/a6952e45afe6f83b21206107341c3c48.avif?t=1745446066 width=800 height=244 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cinematic storytelling:</strong> The story comes to life through stunning cutscenes that highlight key moments in the narrative.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302960/extras/594004afe2edce8e5d9b802bd0159ca9.poster.avif?t=1745446066\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302960/extras/594004afe2edce8e5d9b802bd0159ca9.webm?t=1745446066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302960/extras/594004afe2edce8e5d9b802bd0159ca9.mp4?t=1745446066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>An epic tale of light versus darkness:</strong> Free the lands from terrifying skeleton hordes and restore hope to a world ravaged by war and magic.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategic and tactical battles:</strong> Analyze the battlefield, devise your strategy, and use your heroes’ abilities to find your enemies’ weaknesses and achieve victory, even in the toughest fights.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302960/extras/82bc30710b0de1e6c01962f74405a452.poster.avif?t=1745446066\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302960/extras/82bc30710b0de1e6c01962f74405a452.webm?t=1745446066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3302960/extras/82bc30710b0de1e6c01962f74405a452.mp4?t=1745446066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The fight against the dark army:</strong> Face endless waves of undead skeletons—from simple soldiers to powerful bosses. Each enemy presents unique challenges, making every battle feel distinct.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Atmospheric locations:</strong> Explore the ruins of ancient temples, shadowy forests, dungeons, and lands scorched by darkness.</p></li></ul>",
